3 times in the NE corner, Twice inbetween the DE merchants and the undead tower (a bit closer to DEs than the tower), Once in the NW corner almost out of site down the back side of the steep dune, Once near the western dervs, and once near the eastern dervs north of undead tower.<br>
<br>
